{"tid":1124582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【佔中判決公平？】曹永廉：受影響市民可能家庭破裂、一無所有、法治已死！","createTime":"2019-04-25T06:20:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T08:24:23.000Z","uid":95520,"like":1,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d71cfc90ceb91f9f2746d5443e2501e86dc1908e","tid":1124582,"uid":95520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T06:20:24.000Z","msg":"佔中案今早在西九龍裁判法院判刑，九名被告中只有戴耀廷、陳健民、邵家臻、黃浩銘被判即時入獄，最重僅囚16個月，而判監16個月的朱耀明，以及判囚8個月的鍾耀華和李永達均獲緩刑兩年。至於張秀賢則被判 200小時社會服務令，陳淑莊則因腦部需要動手術，法官押後至6月10日判刑。<br />\n<br />\n對此，藝人曹永廉在《港人講地》Facebook留言稱：「被佔中影響的市民，到現在可能家庭破裂，一無所有，呢個判決公平嗎？法治已死！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.speakout.hk/%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E8%8A%B1%E7%94%9F/43990/-%E4%BD%94%E4%B8%AD%E5%88%A4%E6%B1%BA%E5%85%AC%E5%B9%B3-%E6%9B%B9%E6%B0%B8%E5%BB%89-%E5%8F%97%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E7%A0%B4%E8%A3%82-%E4%B8%80%E7%84%A1%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89-%E6%B3%95%E6%B2%BB%E5%B7%B2%E6%AD%BB-#selected\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.speakout.hk%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%258A%25B1%25E7%2594%259F%2F43990%2F-%25E4%25BD%2594%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2588%25A4%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25B9%25B3-%25E6%259B%25B9%25E6%25B0%25B8%25E5%25BB%2589-%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E9%259F%25BF%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%2583%25BD%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E8%25A3%2582-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%2589%2580%25E6%259C%2589-%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E6%25AD%25BB-%23selected&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5SW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=a79987f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.speakout.hk/%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E8%8A%B1%E7%94%9F/43990/-%E4%BD%94%E4%B8%AD%E5%88%A4%E6%B1%BA%E5%85%AC%E5%B9%B3-%E6%9B%B9%E6%B0%B8%E5%BB%89-%E5%8F%97%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E7%A0%B4%E8%A3%82-%E4%B8%80%E7%84%A1%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89-%E6%B3%95%E6%B2%BB%E5%B7%B2%E6%AD%BB-#selected</a>"},{"pid":"0fc9d4816e991b589bf84